1. *Subotu* smo proveli u parku. (We spent Saturday in the park.)
2. *Subotom* obično idemo u bioskop. (We usually go to the movies on Saturdays.)
3. U *subotu* je koncert. (There is a concert on Saturday.)
4. *Subotu* ćemo provesti u prirodi. (We will spend Saturday in nature.)
5. U *subotu* ujutru ćemo krenuti na izlet. (We will go on a trip on Saturday morning.)
6. *Subotnji* izleti su najbolji. (Saturday trips are the best.)